@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@adminUsername = admin
@employeeUsername = chen_xu
@password = 123456
@repeatableProjectName = delete_project_case_{{$timestamp}}
@forbiddenProjectId = 1
@missingProjectId = 999999
@invalidProjectId = 0

### 提示：正常路径会先创建一个临时项目，再删除它，因此可以重复回放

### 正常路径：管理员登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：管理员创建临时项目
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{repeatableProjectName}}",
  "description": "用于验证删除项目接口的可重复联调用例。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-01",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-30"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatableDeleteProjectId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：管理员删除刚创建的临时项目
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableDeleteProjectId}}

### 正常路径：管理员登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：未登录删除项目，预期 401
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{forbiddenProjectId}}

### 正常路径：普通员工登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{employeeUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：普通员工删除非本人负责项目，预期 403
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{forbiddenProjectId}}

### 正常路径：普通员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：重新登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：project_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{invalidProjectId}}

### 异常路径：项目不存在，预期 404
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{missingProjectId}}
